param.string: CASE  	WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_start_date IN('31-Dec-9999 00:00:00', '01-Jan-0001 00:00:00') OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_start_date IS NULL THEN '01-Jan-1901 00:00:00' ELSE $Aggregation.mvyt24be_start_date END

CASE  	WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date IN('31-Dec-9999 00:00:00', '01-Jan-0001 00:00:00') OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date IS NULL THEN '01-Jan-1901 00:00:00' ELSE $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date END

CASE   	 	 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 1, 1) = 'A' THEN 'asset' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 1, 1) = 'P' THEN 'liability' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 1, 1) = 'O' THEN 'memo' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 1, 1) = 'N' THEN 'capital' 	ELSE 'na'	 END

CASE WHEN $CASHFLOW.accounting_method = 'FVEQ' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '1531%' THEN 'fairValueOCI' ELSE 'amortisedCost' END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_product_group IN ('DEPOSITS', 'DEPOSITS.FLEXIBLE', 'DEMAND.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.HOUSING', 'LOANS', 'COLLECTIONS')   AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date IS NULL THEN 'sight'  	 WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_product_group IN ('DEPOSITS', 'DEPOSITS.FLEXIBLE', 'DEMAND.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.HOUSING', 'LOANS', 'COLLECTIONS')   AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date IS NOT NULL THEN 'term'   ELSE 'na' END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_category_code = '3207' THEN 'mixed' ELSE CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_int_type = 'F' THEN 'fixed' ELSE CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_int_type = 'V' THEN 'floatStandard' ELSE 'na' END END END

CASE  WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica IN ('A04020501','A04040501','A05030201','A05030301','A050401','A050601') THEN 'yes' 	 WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'P0802%' THEN 'yes'  WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'P0804%' THEN 'yes' 	 ELSE 'no' END
CASE  WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'A06%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'O0501%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'O0502%' THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica IN ('O050301','O0604','O0605') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity IN ('STA', 'WAT') THEN 'no' WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity IN ('DOU', 'SUB', 'WRI') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'na' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity IN ('WAT', 'SUB', 'DOU') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity IN ('DOU','SUB','WRI') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
CASE  	WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica = 'P080101' THEN 'yes' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 6) = 'P0504' THEN 'yes'  	ELSE 'no'  END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account IN ('12211001','12221001','12231001') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_risk_type = 'ST1' THEN 'stage1' ELSE CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_risk_type = 'ST2' THEN 'stage2' ELSE CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_risk_type = 'ST3' THEN 'stage3' END END END
CASE WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account, 0, 6) IN ('26403','26404') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'A08%' THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
